      "content": "everything feels so pointless and i'm just so done with everyone telling me to \"push through\" it. can we just talk about it honestly for a sec? like, is it ever actually okay to just give up on everything for good? like, if the pain is just constant, isn't there a point where giving up is the only logical way to find peace?",
